        <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-1 inline-block mb-3">
          <%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p093/output-1743504902093_94_306_279_73.png", alt: "Rette parallele", class: "mx-auto max-w-full rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
        <p>Le <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">rette parallele</span> non si incontrano mai e non hanno nessun punto in comune.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Rette incidenti -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-1 inline-block mb-3">
          <%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p093/output-1743504902093_405_279_279_95.png", alt: "Rette incidenti", class: "mx-auto max-w-full rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
        <p>Le <span class="text-pink-500 dark:text-pink-400 font-bold">rette incidenti</span> si incontrano in un punto. Il piano Ã¨ diviso in due zone piÃ¹ strette e due zone piÃ¹ larghe.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Rette perpendicolari -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-1 inline-block mb-3">
          <%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p093/output-1743504902093_736_213_245_191.png", alt: "Rette perpendicolari", class: "mx-auto max-w-full rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
        <p>Le <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold">rette perpendicolari</span> si incontrano in un punto. Il piano Ã¨ diviso in quattro parti uguali.</p>
