    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 1 -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        1
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <strong>Colora le rette di blu se sono <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">parallele</span>, di rosa se sono <span class="text-pink-500 dark:text-pink-400">incidenti</span>, di verde se sono <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">perpendicolari</span>.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
      <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-1 inline-block">
        <%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p093/output-1743504902093_133_593_832_207.png", alt: "Esercizio rette", class: "max-w-full rounded-lg" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MateVIVA -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-4 border-green-400 dark:border-green-500 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 mb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks auto-advance">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold">mate VIVA</span>
      <span class="font-bold text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">RETTE... CHE CONOSCI!</span>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4"><strong>ðŸ”´ Osserva le immagini e scrivi il tipo di rette che vedi.</strong></p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6">
      <!-- Immagine 1: Ombrellone + Scaffale con 2 input -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-1 inline-block mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p093/output-1743504902093_154_943_524_140.png", alt: "Ombrellone e Scaffale", class: "max-w-full rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 w-full justify-center">
          <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="incidenti"
